text: @GeoRebekah On Sunday, Florida officials reported 3,494 confirmed cases. What people don't know is the Florida Health Department have their own report that keeps getting deleted which confirms 4,671 cases. This is a serious problem and must be taken seriously. #COVID19 #coronavirus
